=head1 DESCRIPTION

Enable custom Time to Live (TTL) settings for rows and columns without
setting a TTL default for the specified table.

For more information, see Enabling TTL on tables
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/keyspaces/latest/devguide/TTL-how-it-works.html#ttl-howitworks_enabling)
in the I<Amazon Keyspaces Developer Guide>.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Status => Str

Shows how to enable custom Time to Live (TTL) settings for the
specified table.



